transbit.tbits.config
Class FBField

java.lang.Object
  transbit.tbits.config.FBField
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class FBField
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

FBField is a conceptual union that represent different types of fields in a form. An FBField object can hold the details of one such field at a time. The type of the field is determined by the FBFieldType enum value of the FBField object.
